I used to play on SZ.  I can say mages are at best irritating not lethal.  Some of the better mages that have wristband of secrets fight with a great deal of lethality.  The majority of SZ is under geared as well so a mage stands a better chance there as opposed to the other zek servers.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=486389" target="_blank" class="postlink">Farrudar the Noob Poon</a>
