				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Heh, from talks with Rytan, PvP changes are not likely to occur until OoW is out and all the bugs ironed out.
<br />

<br />
That said, actively raiding high end mages:
<br />

<br />
Siclid
<br />
Mearis
<br />
Ginafae
<br />

<br />
That is it.
<br />

<br />
Mages are not quite as bad as everyone paints them, from a spell point of view.  Bolts are very deadly, but the problem is some classes are way overpowered, like rangers, necromancers and bards, and nobody can hope to go against any of those one on one and live.
<br />

<br />
That said, pet damage in PvP is a joke right now and should be fixed, but the problem is more with some classes being overpowered than other mages being underpowered.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
